General.Name: Centor Energy Inc
General.Description: Centor Energy, Inc. develops and explores oil shale projects in Canada. The company owns a 55% working interest in SHA0011 and SHA0013 oil shale leases covering an area of approximately 21,658 gross acres in Pasquia Hills Saskatchewan. The company was formerly known as Centor, Inc. and changed its name to Centor Energy, Inc. in December 2013. Centor Energy, Inc. was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Calgary, Canada.
